 <div class="story">  <p>The Breakers is an oceanfront condominium complex consisting of 10 units in the heart of Kill Devil Hills. You will find shopping and dining withinn walking distance of the Breakers and a variety of unit sizes with 1, 2 and 3 bedroom units and most of the units have ocean views. The ocean front pool and the boardwalk to the beach are maintained by the home owners association. The Breakers are located just south of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KillDevilHills/ocean-acres.asp" title="Ocean Acres">Ocean Acres</a> subdivision and north of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/nags head/nags-head-shore.asp" title="Nags Head Shores">Nags Head Shores</a>. </p> 
